<li class="list-item nav-item-tracking"><a class="color-red uppercase js-clickTrack" href="/ct/topics/" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="All Topics & People">All Topics &amp; People</a></li></ul></li><li class="nav-column w-150"><h5 class="heading-xs uppercase align-left spacer-bottom-15"><a href="/ct/help/">Help & Info</a></h5><ul class="list"><li class="list-item"><a class="nav_link js-clickTrack" href="https://help.christianitytoday.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=360002884954" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Contact Us">Contact Us</a> | <a class="nav_link js-clickTrack" href="https://help.christianitytoday.com/hc/en-us/categories/360003170773-Christianity-Today" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="FAQ">FAQ</a></li><li class="list-item"><a class="nav_link js-clickTrack" href="/account" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="My Account">My Account</a></li><li class="list-item"><a class="nav_link js-clickTrack" href="/ct/help/sitemap.html" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="Site Map">Site Map</a></li><li class="list-item"><a class="nav_link js-clickTrack" href="https://ctmagazine.myshopify.com/" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Explore" data-label="CT Store">Store</a></li><li class="list-item nav-item-tracking"><a href="/ct/newsletters" class="color-red uppercase js-clickTrack" target="_blank" data-category="NL Sub" data-action="/ct/2023/october-web-only/israel-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html" data-label="Sections Header List Item">Free Newsletters</a><div class="follow-us d-flex align-items-center spacer-top-5 spacer-inner-top-10"><figure class="spacer-right-10"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/CTMagazine" target="_blank"><img width="16" height="16" title="Facebook" alt="Facebook" src="/system/img/icon_facebook.svg" /></a></figure><figure class="spacer-right-10"><a href="https://twitter.com