</span></div><div class="meta-container " itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><h1 class="title article-title" itemprop="name">American Christians Should Stand with Israel under Attack</h1><div class="deck spacer-top-20 spacer-bottom-15" itemprop="description">While we pray for peace, we need moral clarity about this war.</div>
<div class="article-byline "><span class="author" itemprop="author">Russell Moore</span><span class="pipe">|</span><span class="postdate" itemprop="datePublished"><time datetime="2023-10-7">October 7, 2023 </time></span></div>
<div class="article-languages spacer-top-5"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section><section class="article-featured-image "><div class="container"><figure class="p-relative align-center spacer-top-40"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/136651.jpg?h=528&w=940" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/136651.jpg?w=1880 2x" width="940" alt="American Christians Should Stand with Israel under Attack" title="American Christians Should Stand with Israel under Attack" /></figure><figcaption class="spacer-top-5 spacer-bottom-5"><div class="credit ">
									Image:
									
										Amir Levy / Stringer / Getty Images News
									</div>
<div class="caption spacer-top-10 ">A Tel Aviv building damaged by a missile from the Gaza Strip.</div>
</figcaption></div></section><section class="container"><div class="spacer-top-25 u-cf social-nav-item"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/system/social/css/share.css?09262023"></link>
				<div
					class="ctSocialShare ctSocialShare_horizontal ctSocialShare_fallback"
