				><ul><li class="ctSocialShare_facebook shareCount"><a class="js-shareLinks" target="_blank" onclick="window.open('http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2023%2foctober-web-only%2fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%3futm_medium%3dwidgetsocial', 'newwindow', 'width=520, height=670'); return false;" href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2023%2foctober-web-only%2fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%3futm_medium%3dwidgetsocial&title=American+Christians+Should+Stand+with+Israel+under+Attack" title="Share on Facebook" data-provider="facebook"><span>
													SHARE
												</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_twitter shareCount"><a class="js-shareLinks" target="_blank" onclick="window.open('https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2023%2foctober-web-only%2fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%3futm_medium%3dwidgetsocial&via=CTMagazine&text=American+Christians+Should+Stand+with+Israel+under+Attack&counturl=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2023%2foctober-web-only%2fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%3futm_medium%3dwidgetsocial&sharetext=American+Christians+Should+Stand+with+Israel+under+Attack+via+%40CTMagazine', 'newwindow', 'width=500, height=350'); return false;" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2023%2foctober-web-only%2fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%3futm_medium%3dwidgetsocial&via=CTMagazine&text=American+Christians+Should+Stand+with+Israel+under+Attack&counturl=https%3a%2f%2fwww.christianitytoday.com%2fct%2f2023%2foctober-web-only%2fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%3futm_medium%3dwidgetsocial&sharetext=American+Christians+Should+Stand+with+Israel+under+Attack+via+%40CTMagazine" title="Share on X"><span>post</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_whatsapp"><a class="js-shareLinks" target="_blank" href="https://web.whatsapp.com/send?text=https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2023/october-web-only/israel-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html?utm_source%3dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3dwidgetsocial%26utm_campaign%3dCT" title="Share on WhatsApp" data-provider="whatsapp"><span>Share</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_share"><a class="js-shareLink js-trackJanrainClick linkVar" href="https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2023/october-web-only/israel-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html?utm_medium=widgetsocial" data-modalid="shareUrlModal" data-shareurl="https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2023/october-web-only/israel-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html?utm_medium=widgetsocial" dat